td.div: English: A detailed Robinson projection SVG map with grouping enabled to connect all non-contiguous parts of a country's territory for easy colouring. Smaller countries can also be represented by larger circles to show their data easier. A thorough description of use and other instructions relating to can be found on the instruction page.
